family plans to fly to israel he said 
after getting settled in israel the family plans to make their 
first trip to the united states to visit friends 
the latest in a series of snags that held up ms shurukhts 
emigration was that her mother refused to sign a form saying her 
daughter did not have any financial obligations to her abe stolar 
said the mother apparently has now signed the form 
