the incident at the zhejiang agriculture university in hangzhou 
took place against the backdrop of continued antiblack 
demonstrations in nanking where chinese students are demanding that 
african students involved in a christmas eve brawl be punished 
martin ayuk a student from cameroon said the problems in 
